{"tid":2087570,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【Minecraft Server】我諗住試下做香港版2b2t。(2)","createTime":"2020-06-30T17:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T08:10:21.000Z","uid":75250,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb51ad1a7575c219552866ca83bc8a80d4889b3","tid":2087570,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgegYZT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgegYZT.png&h=77a2f5ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊post : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1925477/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1925477/page/1</a><br />\n由於之前個post已經沉咗睇推唔返，所以開咗新post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下就係原本個post開始個介紹(雖然改咗啲嘢)<br />\n<br />\n話就話想做香港版2b2t啫，但當然唔想好似山寨咁用返人哋個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就改咗<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">大笪地伺服器</span></strong>呢個名。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">IP : <a href=\"http://dddmc.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdddmc.hk&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=801b82d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">dddmc.hk</a></span></strong><br />\nDiscord : <a href=\"https://discord.gg/Nt6V5nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FNt6V5nf&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=22b788c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/Nt6V5nf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://minecraft-mp.com/banner-247280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fminecraft-mp.com%2Fbanner-247280.png&h=b79526cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://minecraft-statistic.net/en/userbars/560x90/server/241500.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fminecraft-statistic.net%2Fen%2Fuserbars%2F560x90%2Fserver%2F241500.png&h=80961341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個server基本上<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三不管</span></strong>，你同admin講話有人用外掛或者整爛你啲嘢特登殺你都唔會有人理你。<br />\n換句話說，你做乜都得。(除咗起lag machine)<br />\n亦都<strong>冇得tp</strong>，所以要靠睇坐標做人。<br />\n個server<strong>開24</strong>，除非受到乜嘢刺激，如果唔係應該唔會收皮。<br />\n而且有<strong>隨機重生</strong>，唔使驚畀人spawn-kill。<br />\n雖然話就話可以用外掛，但係某幾種因為Lag Server所以禁止咗。<br />\n(詳細入discord睇公告)<br />\n如果個server有啲乜嘢三七廿一，到時就會有公告出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ut5b9kh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUt5b9kh.png&h=3c2a6c4c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zwyk2Fh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwyk2Fh.png&h=120eee83&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n個spawn已經同第一個post嗰陣時唔同曬，所以脫離spawn唯有祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c436ba9f0e7693b847e9b5ea77cd119ec9f688","tid":2087570,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"*Blog (2020-07-01)<br />\n<strong>-Server升級至版本1.16.1</strong><br />\nServer在今日凌晨零時升級至版本1.16.1，升級後可能會出現不穩定情況及故障，敬請留意。<br />\n如有任何與升級版本相關的大改動，將會再作公告。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>-有關國安法</strong><br />\n港區國安法已於昨晚(30/6)晚上十一時生效。<br />\n有鑑及此，伺服器將會繼續維持服務直至被另行通告。<br />\n<br />\n本伺服器已維持開放快四個月，可見將來伺服器仍可維持運作。<br />\n感謝各位在期間支持及遊玩，並希望各位能夠繼續開心暢玩。<br />\n<br />\n下次更新：~九月至十二月<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a956ec23ddd22fd0fdd68878e99d8c14b996d331","tid":2087570,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a05953209961f2277876f03fb919e9f0fd41bd59","tid":2087570,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71ff6ba26c45def18bb72b656d30bcdfaf2bb478","tid":2087570,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"340e7f456675385e81d087940a581809ffa247be","tid":2087570,"uid":75250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor